{"tid":1788524,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發行動post] 日程表上面冇呀，快啲入嚟幫手推到個個都知","createTime":"2019-12-18T17:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T00:18:55.000Z","uid":209717,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f212fa8a617e9a0d18d037f76bd7b44460129159","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLNRkwp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLNRkwp.jpg&h=f45081a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CU0Yh4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CU0Yh4.jpg&h=b46d1270&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyDdyRp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyDdyRp.jpg&h=53b20540&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7WR4X5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7WR4X5.jpg&h=983e3e17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2B6TRq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2B6TRq.jpg&h=48d22905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">20 DEC 2019 星期五全民口罩日</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人人都做到!!!!香港人一齊嚟參加!!!!<br />\n<br />\n同埋幫手轉發出去<br />\n星星之火 可以燎原，唔好睇少你自己既力量🔥🔥🔥<br />\n星期五，全民口罩!!<br />\n<br />\ntg channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/wewillnotforget1220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwewillnotforget1220&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6gsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f551910f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wewillnotforget1220</a>"},{"pid":"35d4ccf9d6784c2bd640248bdbb9e0f24edc6b06","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:37:56.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"802a6d348794b03534df9ed4f0baa4f8d6135110","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:38:21.000Z","msg":"快啲幫手推 <br />\n人人戴口罩呀"},{"pid":"52f262358ca8878165707a3596b11bf83af43f9a","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:39:11.000Z","msg":"全民口罩日 <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊嘅星期五，唔洗做得多，一齊帶個口罩出街<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問: 禁蒙面法撤回咗喇喎，仲帶嚟做咩？<br />\n<br />\n全民口罩除咗想表達對禁蒙面法嘅反抗，更係想以口罩為記，比同路人感受我地都仲係度抗爭緊，堅持緊&amp;互相勉勵, 仲要俾被捕同離開咗嘅手足知道，我地從來都冇忘記佢地<br />\n<br />\n當手足一齊戴起個口罩去表態，其實就已經可以凝聚力量，去話比呢個政權同手足聽，我地仍然堅持五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n呢個活動門檻同成本都唔高，最多都係比幾蚊買口罩 （你屋企應該有啦係咪？）<br />\n就算你係上班一族、學生、中年人都可以一齊響應下<br />\n<br />\n如果你認同活動理念，請你用fb/ig/tg post或者airdrop將呢一個活動分享比身邊嘅人，邀請佢地一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n星期五一齊帶口罩出街！"},{"pid":"1a1d88e0af80f075982cb913595ac25fde9807a4","tid":1788524,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c97080c7c3ac23a2842ba6be90957418374e6ff","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"全民口罩日Q&amp;A⁉️<br />\n<br />\n1. 戴口罩有咩用？🔅<br />\n可以鼓勵同路人，<br />\n想令到大家習慣行多一步，將抗爭成為日常生活嘅一部分，成為習慣<br />\n（抗爭日常化好處詳見下一篇文）<br />\n<br />\n2. 上幾次口罩日都冇人響應，點解我今次要帶？🔅<br />\n大家唔幫手宣傳，冇咩人知就冇人帶<br />\n但如果一齊宣傳，可能就會有唔同呢？<br />\n我地肯花時間出嚟遊行，但就連帶口罩咁低成本都做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n如果真係驚條街冇人帶，可以考慮帶定2個口罩出街<br />\n比自己之餘都可以比身邊嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n3. 我唔想比人標籤🏷️🔅<br />\n如果唔想明顯表態，可以考慮係返工放工嘅路程先帶口罩支持<br />\n呢排天氣都凍，病咗要帶口罩都唔奇呀<br />\n<br />\n4. 我怕帶口罩會比狗逗🔅<br />\n我地有帶口罩嘅自由<br />\n同埋身上冇野，都冇野可以入你啦<br />\n唔洗幫手製造白色恐怖啦🙏🏻"},{"pid":"963a9befe61b046647f2b6c774bb8ea86c6ed5a2","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"推到個個都睇到"},{"pid":"ccfa448530e1d5e09557397121aa70b62955ab52","tid":1788524,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"239d0659c5cb50f4746f1a0813f23082b2c295a8","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:49:52.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"4a518e7768113467b4d2af1a948c0674e53a04be","tid":1788524,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T17:56:52.000Z","msg":"推呀 要個個都知"},{"pid":"54f2957cbb3f82558d5f2016b6c0cd1d06ae9885","tid":1788524,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6gsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=01e74750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6gsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=34586f9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8fdfb002d33ce4d73fdf95d3274f98475688a21e","tid":1788524,"uid":199720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:30:39.000Z","msg":"小弟文宣po 幫幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n突發 我宣布今個聖誕不再孤獨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1788548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1788548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d622e30191e068fc3ff2f5b6e69e04d32698afdf","tid":1788524,"uid":199720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f0d73265bd1f5861ded69442e377f5c149ac1c7",